{"id": "1512741681487941692", "channel_id": "1505167541818101862", "type": 0, "author_id": "594196021119287316", "author_name": "nemu_s_t_a_r", "author_bot": false, "content": "那天，透過玻璃看著裡面的商品，我指著其中一個最可愛的娃娃，然後對著旁邊的服務生說：「我要這個。」\n結果那個服務生回：「先生，這裡是育嬰室，不是百貨公司。」", "timestamp": "2026-06-06T08:55:22.248000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "6️⃣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1505167541818101862", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.5.1.0 停服维护公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881"}
